properties.name: Description
properties.sample:
MATERIAL UNIT OF MEASURE COMMON FORMAT:
For each of the different forms (units of measure) in which the material may be available, includes  dimensions of the material (different ways to measure the height, length and width) as well as the weight of the material at that specific unit of measure. This describes the expected/planned Uniot of measure for a country at a category level.
